import App from './views/App.marko'
import Home from '/views/pages/home'
import NotFound from '/views/pages/404'
 
const Routes = [
    { name: 'home', path: '/', component: Home },
    { name: '404', path: '/not-found', component: NotFound },
    // ... 

    /* Add any other page you want:
        Check https://www.npmjs.com/package/marko-router5
        for the documentation about how to install and configure routes
    */
]
 
App.renderSync({ Routes }).prependTo( document.body )
